data.description: Take a walk inside this gem & see for yourself! Bright, airy and COMPLETELY REDONE with attention to detail... This 3 bedroom, 3 Full bath Sonata Model with 2nd floor Loft features: Dramatic open Living room/Dining room concept freshly painted neutral color, chic rectangular style Plank floors thru out lower level w/ New carpeting too. Elegance & coziness truly shines thru! Vaulted ceilings and the walls of windows allows natural light in accented with brilliant high hats! Everything is " BRAND NEW" from ceiling fans, light fixtures, wall socket covers, brushed nickel door hinges and door handles, new A/C Condenser for 2nd floor and so much more... The gourmet kitchen is beautifully presented with all new S/S appliances, deco lighting, NEW white wood cabinets (soft close) complete with drawer and cabinet knobs that compliment the S/S appliances for both style and functionality, New quartz white with grey vein counter tops, double door butler pantry, large eat in area with many windows for natural light...truly a chefs dream! 1st floor Master suite with 2 walk in closets, accented tray ceiling & a unique tiled bathroom with large walk in shower surrounded by NEW seamless glass shower doors, large Jacuzzi tub, double vanity sink complete this spa inspired vibe. 2nd bedroom on 1st floor with new carpeting is nearby a 2nd FULL redone bathroom perfect for guests! A dedicated laundry room with NEW washer, dryer is a nice touch for all. Up on to the 2nd floor you will find a spacious loft, a 3rd bedroom and a Full bathroom. There is a bonus walk in utility room with a finished large additional storage area. Home is freshly painted with new carpeting thru out. 2 zoned AC and heat. New expanded patio on back of home. 2 car garage with freshly painted walls and floors epoxied with speckle paint. The HOA covers lawn care, snow removal and trash. Enjoy some fun time with jogging path, pool, bocce and more here at Horizon at Barnegat. Close to LBI beaches, marinas, shopping, restaurants, and Atlantic City. Come envision your new beginning while it's still available. 30 X 13 patio prior to closing will be poured (cement in rear). See neighbor next door look out back door #17 Duxbury same will be provided soon as weather permits pouring. Association approved privacy trees surrounding patio. Seller to install trees prior to closing.
